  questionText: What is the superficial layer of a unit?
  revealAnswerOnIncorrect: 1
  numOptions: 4
  correctAnswer: The surface of a unit after it has been cleaned of any later vegetation
    and smaller rocks.
  incorrectAnswers:
  - The layer after you being excavation.
  - The layer of the unit after you have backfilled.
  - The bottom layer after excavation is completed.
